title: Ronda Rousey
summary: Ronda Jean Rousey (/ˈraʊzi/;[12] born February 1, 1987) is an American professional wrestler, actress, former judoka and former mixed martial artist. She is best known for her time in the UFC and the WWE.[13] Her longstanding nickname, "Rowdy", was inherited from late professional wrestler Roddy Piper.[1] Rousey has not wrestled since she took time off from WWE after WrestleMania in April 2019.
